name: A10 Headset - XB - Grey/Green | Dell USA
description: Gear up to push into enemy territory and show them no mercy. Take your gear to the next level with the Special Edition Call of Duty A10 Headset. Durable construction and extended comfort to combat fatigue means you can game longer, play better, and show the enemy what you’re made of. “Tuned for Gaming” with ASTRO Audio gives you 40mm drivers so you can hear your game and your teammates with clarity and precision. Game:Voice Balancing, uni-directional mic, in-line volume control, and flip-to-mute functionality delivers total control of your gaming audio experience.
